Comments.Message:
It looks like you may have two copies of the TypeScript binaries installed, somehow. Can you try uninstalling all TypeScript-related things (extensions, entries in the Programs and Features control panel), reinstalling, and see what happens?

If that doesn't fix it, please re-open this bug with the new ActivityLog.xml so we can try to diagnose further. Thanks!
